original: Enbom, Sven Albert, tandläkare, Vänersborg, f. 27/2/12 i Norrtälje av civ:ing. Albert E. o. Ehn Korn. G. 42 m. Kerstin Ottkärr. Barn: Håkan f. 43, Birgitta 45. — S;tud:ex. v. Gbgs h. latin 31, stud. v. Karol. inst., med. kand. v. Lunds univ. 34, tandl. 38. Prakt, i Vargön o. Vänersborg.
translated: Enbom, Sven Albert, dentist, Vänersborg, b. February 27th, 1912 in Norrtälje to civil engineer Albert E. and Ehn Korn. Married in 1942 to Kerstin Ottkärr. Children: Håkan b. 1943, Birgitta b. 1945. Educational background: Completed secondary education with a focus on Latin in Gothenburg in 1931, studied at the Karolinska Institute, earned a bachelor's degree in medicine from Lund University in 1934, and graduated with a degree in dentistry in 1938. Practiced in Vargön and Vänersborg.
